# Scripts and Interactivity Guide

## Script Organization

- Client-side scripts are located in [src/scripts/](mdc:src/scripts/)
- Each script handles a specific interactive feature
- Scripts are organized by functionality

## Key Scripts

- [navLinkManager.ts](mdc:src/scripts/components/navLinkManager.ts): Navigation link management
- [preloader.ts](mdc:src/scripts/components/preloader.ts): Page preloader functionality
- [mouse-cursor.ts](mdc:src/scripts/components/mouse-cursor.ts): Custom mouse cursor effects
- [totop-button.ts](mdc:src/scripts/components/totop-button.ts): Scroll to top button
- [obfuscateEmail.ts](mdc:src/scripts/components/obfuscateEmail.ts): Email obfuscation

## Script Integration

- Scripts are loaded via [BasicScripts.astro](mdc:src/components/BasicScripts.astro)
- Use TypeScript for type safety
- Follow existing patterns for DOM manipulation and event handling

## Performance Considerations

- Keep scripts lightweight and focused
- Use event delegation where appropriate
- Minimize DOM queries and manipulations
